text: John Skinner (c. 1535 – 1584), of Reigate, Surrey was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Reigate in 1559 and 1572. ==References== Category:1535 births Category:1584 deaths Category:People from Reigate Category:English MPs 1559 Category:English MPs 1572–1583
